---
import Layout from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const lastUpdated = '2026-04-23';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy — Greg Maxfield"
  description="Privacy policy for gregmaxfield.com — covering analytics, email collection, cookies, and your rights."
>
  <section style="padding-top: 3rem; padding-bottom: 3rem;">
    <div class="container content-narrow">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p style="color: var(--text-muted, #888); font-size: 0.9rem;">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <p>
        This privacy policy explains how gregmaxfield.com collects, uses, and protects information
        when you visit this site. I take your privacy seriously and collect only what's necessary
        to understand how the site is used and to communicate with readers who opt in.
      </p>

      <h2>Information Collected</h2>

      <h3>Analytics (Google Analytics)</h3>
      <p>
        This site uses Google Analytics (ID: G-BNVECLV39M) to understand how visitors use the site —
        which pages are read, how long visitors stay, and where traffic comes from. Google Analytics
        collects data such as your IP address (anonymized), browser type, device type, and pages visited.
        This data is processed by Google and subject to{' '}
        <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.
        You can opt out of Google Analytics by installing the{' '}
        <a href="https://tools.google.com/dlpage/gaoptout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Google Analytics Opt-out Browser Add-on
        </a>.
      </p>

      <h3>Email Collection (Kit / ConvertKit)</h3>
      <p>
        If you subscribe to updates or a newsletter through this site, your email address is collected
        and stored by Kit (formerly ConvertKit). Providing your email is entirely voluntary. You can
        unsubscribe at any time using the unsubscribe link included in every email. Kit's privacy
        practices are governed by the{' '}
        <a href="https://kit.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Kit Privacy Policy</a>.
      </p>

      <h3>Vercel Analytics</h3>
      <p>
        This site is hosted on Vercel, which may collect anonymized performance and usage data as part
        of its infrastructure. See the{' '}
        <a href="https://vercel.com/legal/privacy-policy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Vercel Privacy Policy
        </a>{' '}
        for details.
      </p>

      <h2>Cookies</h2>
      <p>
        This site uses cookies primarily for analytics purposes (Google Analytics) and to maintain
        session state. No advertising or cross-site tracking cookies are used. You can control cookies
        through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect some site functionality.
      </p>

      <h2>Information Sharing</h2>
      <p>
        I do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties, except as described
        above (Google Analytics, Kit). Your data is never used for advertising targeting.
      </p>

      <h2>Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        Analytics data is retained according to the default retention periods set by Google Analytics
        (26 months). Email subscriber data is retained until you unsubscribe or request deletion.
      </p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>
        Depending on your location, you may have rights regarding your personal data under applicable
        privacy laws, including:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <strong>CCPA (California):</strong> The right to know what personal information is collected,
          the right to delete personal information, and the right to opt out of the sale of personal
          information. This site does not sell personal information.
        </li>
        <li>
          <strong>GDPR (European Union / UK):</strong> The right to access, rectify, erase, restrict,
          or port your personal data, and the right to object to processing.
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        To exercise any of these rights, or to request deletion of your data, contact me at{' '}
        <a href="mailto:greg@gregmaxfield.com">greg@gregmaxfield.com</a>.
      </p>

      <h2>External Links</h2>
      <p>
        This site contains links to external websites (Substack, Amazon, Bookshop.org, etc.). This
        privacy policy applies only to gregmaxfield.com. Please review the privacy policies of any
        external sites you visit.
      </p>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>
        This site is not directed at children under 13 and does not knowingly collect personal
        information from children.
      </p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>
        This policy may be updated occasionally. The "last updated" date at the top of this page
        reflects the most recent revision.
      </p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>
        Questions about this privacy policy? Reach me at{' '}
        <a href="mailto:greg@gregmaxfield.com">greg@gregmaxfield.com</a> or through the{' '}
        <a href="/about">About page</a>.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
